### ============================================
### 시스템 상태 및 헬스체크
### ============================================

### Actuator 헬스체크
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Actuator 메트릭
GET {{host}}/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Actuator 정보
GET {{host}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

### 트레이딩 헬스체크
GET {{host}}/api/trading/health
Accept: application/json

### 거래 활성화 상태 확인
GET {{host}}/api/trading/enabled
Accept: application/json
